        <Parent_String>interior lighting [300052027], lighting by location or context [300052011], lighting [300051944], systems by function [300242038], systems (equipment) [300008550], Object Groupings and Systems (hierarchy name) [300241489], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
